{"tid":566374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以蝻制蝻~南亞漢街頭遇劫 遭兩賊搶走萬多元","createTime":"2018-02-20T01:22:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T01:22:47.000Z","uid":65346,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b02cd5303208eabcb58633b1145826e41fb79c73","tid":566374,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T01:22:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180220/57852169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F57852169&d=zPblo4S34Y2ngGBY31oUIgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7978245e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F57852169&h=08365633\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180220/57852169</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中環美利道與金鐘道交界，凌晨零時許，一名42歲南亞裔男子，在街頭遭兩名同鄉打劫，搶去約15,000元現金。賊人得手後逃去無蹤，事主稍後報警，由警員到場調查，案件暫列行劫，交中區警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。"}]}